Help on skill: bravery
Skill type: defensive
Usage duration: 14 rounds

Normally, all the front line members in a party will take hits.
Bravery allows one to protect the other frontline party members
from taking melee hits. This is useful when working with less
experienced defenders.
You can modify the efficiency of the skill. Default is 100%.

Example, if you want to use your skill at 60% efficiency:
	use bravery at 60

